_header: Here I conclude all my making
_description: John Audelay, An exhortation — thirty-four 13-line stanzas

BodDou302.First Lines:
Here I conclud al my makyngIn þe merce of god I haue sayd be
                    fore…
BodDou302.Last Lines:
…Bot vche mon mend hym selue fore chameȝif ȝe deme
                    mys ȝe wil be chent
